#: ../../concepts.md:3
msgid "Understanding spatial transcriptomics analysis."
msgstr "理解空间转录组分析。"

#: ../../concepts.md:7
msgid "What is Spatial Transcriptomics?"
msgstr "什么是空间转录组？"

#: ../../concepts.md:9
msgid ""
"Spatial transcriptomics measures gene expression while preserving the "
"physical location of cells in tissue. Unlike standard single-cell RNA "
"sequencing, it tells you **where** cells are, not just what they express."
msgstr ""
"空间转录组在保留组织中细胞物理位置的同时测量基因表达。与传统单细胞 RNA 测序不同，它告诉你细胞**在哪里**，而不只是表达什么。"

#: ../../concepts.md:11
msgid ""
"**Key insight**: Location matters. A tumor cell behaves differently "
"depending on whether it's surrounded by immune cells or fibroblasts."
msgstr ""
"**关键洞见**：位置很重要。肿瘤细胞的行为会随着其周围是免疫细胞还是成纤维细胞而改变。"

#: ../../concepts.md:15
msgid "Core Analysis Types"
msgstr "核心分析类型"

#: ../../concepts.md:17
msgid "Spatial Domains"
msgstr "空间区域"

#: ../../concepts.md:19
msgid ""
"**What it does**: Groups tissue regions based on similar gene expression "
"patterns."
msgstr "**作用**：基于相似的基因表达模式对组织区域进行分组。"

#: ../../concepts.md:21
msgid ""
"**When to use**: First step after preprocessing. Identifies tissue "
"architecture like tumor regions, immune infiltrates, or tissue layers."
msgstr ""
"**何时使用**：预处理后的第一步。用于识别组织结构，如肿瘤区域、免疫浸润区或组织分层。"

