#: ../../concepts.md:43
msgid "**Rule of thumb**:"
msgstr "**经验法则**："

#: ../../concepts.md:44
msgid "**Xenium, MERFISH, CosMx**: Use annotation (single-cell resolution)"
msgstr "**Xenium、MERFISH、CosMx**：用注释（单细胞分辨率）"

#: ../../concepts.md:45
msgid "**Visium, Slide-seq**: Use deconvolution (multiple cells per spot)"
msgstr "**Visium、Slide-seq**：用去卷积（每个 spot 多细胞）"

#: ../../concepts.md:49
msgid "Cell Communication"
msgstr "细胞通讯"

#: ../../concepts.md:51
msgid ""
"**What it does**: Identifies which cell types are \"talking\" to each other "
"through ligand-receptor interactions."
msgstr "**作用**：通过配体-受体相互作用识别哪些细胞类型在相互“对话”。"

#: ../../concepts.md:53
msgid ""
"**Key concept**: Cell A expresses a ligand (signal molecule), Cell B "
"expresses the receptor. If they're spatially close, they may be "
"communicating."
msgstr ""
"**关键概念**：细胞 A 表达配体（信号分子），细胞 B 表达受体；如果它们空间上足够接近，可能存在通讯。"

#: ../../concepts.md:55
msgid "**Species matters**: Use the correct database:"
msgstr "**物种很重要**：请选择正确的数据库："

#: ../../concepts.md:56
msgid "Human: `liana_resource=\"consensus\"`"
msgstr "人类：`liana_resource=\"consensus\"`"

#: ../../concepts.md:57
msgid "Mouse: `liana_resource=\"mouseconsensus\"`"
msgstr "小鼠：`liana_resource=\"mouseconsensus\"`"

#: ../../concepts.md:61
msgid "RNA Velocity"
msgstr "RNA Velocity（RNA 速度）"

#: ../../concepts.md:63
msgid ""
"**What it does**: Predicts future cell states by comparing spliced vs "
"unspliced RNA."
msgstr "**作用**：通过比较 spliced 与 unspliced RNA 预测未来的细胞状态。"

#: ../../concepts.md:65
msgid ""
"**Key insight**: If a gene has more unspliced RNA, it's being upregulated. "
"If more spliced, it's being downregulated. This tells you the \"direction\" "
"cells are moving."
msgstr ""
"**关键洞见**：如果某基因的 unspliced RNA 更多，通常表示正在上调；如果 spliced 更多，表示正在下调。这反映了细胞变化的“方向”。"

#: ../../concepts.md:67
msgid ""
"**Requirement**: Your data must have `spliced` and `unspliced` layers (from "
"velocyto, kallisto, or STARsolo)."
msgstr ""
"**要求**：数据中必须包含 `spliced` 与 `unspliced` layers（来自 velocyto、kallisto 或 STARsolo）。"

