msgid "1. Skipping Preprocessing"
msgstr "1. 跳过预处理"

#: ../../concepts.md:140
msgid ""
"Most analyses fail because preprocessing wasn't run. Always preprocess first:"
msgstr "很多分析失败是因为没有运行预处理。务必先预处理："

#: ../../concepts.md:145
msgid "2. Wrong Species Parameter"
msgstr "2. 物种参数错误"

#: ../../concepts.md:147
msgid "Cell communication analysis requires correct species:"
msgstr "细胞通讯分析需要正确的物种设置："

#: ../../concepts.md:156
msgid "3. Expecting Single-Cell Resolution from Visium"
msgstr "3. 指望 Visium 提供单细胞分辨率"

#: ../../concepts.md:158
msgid ""
"Visium spots contain 1-10 cells. Use deconvolution to estimate proportions, "
"not annotation to assign types."
msgstr "Visium 的一个 spot 含 1–10 个细胞。请用去卷积估计比例，而不是用注释强行赋予单一类型。"

#: ../../concepts.md:160
msgid "4. Using GPU Methods Without GPU"
msgstr "4. 没有 GPU 却使用依赖 GPU 的方法"

#: ../../concepts.md:162
msgid "Methods like Cell2location are 10-100x slower without GPU. Either:"
msgstr "像 Cell2location 这类方法在没有 GPU 时会慢 10–100 倍。你可以："

#: ../../concepts.md:163
msgid "Set `use_gpu=False` explicitly"
msgstr "显式设置 `use_gpu=False`"

#: ../../concepts.md:164
msgid "Use CPU-friendly alternatives (FlashDeconv, RCTD)"
msgstr "使用更适合 CPU 的替代方案（FlashDeconv、RCTD）"

